title: Fendi Medium Peekaboo ISeeU
description: Fendi medium Peekaboo ISeeU handbag in white calfskin leather. Featuring gold-toned hardware, single flat handle, and classic twist-lock closures at front and back. The top opens to light pink soft nappa leather lining two compartments separated by a stiff partition. Approx dimensions: 33cm(B-L) x 24cm(H) x 12(D), handle drop 11.5cm, adjustable and detachable strap drop 54cm. Accompanied by Fendi dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
